{"id": "1401012780265373708", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "924665171010551869", "author_name": "cucudas.", "author_bot": false, "content": "모방결정체 > 에이지스, 동야추억 > 현석파편. 전 이렇게는 무조건 사는 것 같아요", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:24:36.374000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍🏻", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1401012943906406530", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "924665171010551869", "author_name": "cucudas.", "author_bot": false, "content": "에깃스는 쓰임새가 많고, 오리타는 가끔 쓰임새가 있고, 에리카는 캐릭 늘리기용 말곤 쓰임새가 없었어서", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:25:15.389000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1401013144062660669", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "924665171010551869", "author_name": "cucudas.", "author_bot": false, "content": "초반엔는 구슬이 많으실 수도 있는데, 나중엔 구슬 얻을 곧이 환몽심잠밖에 없어서 다 못사실거에요", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:26:03.110000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1401013198517178518", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "924665171010551869", "author_name": "cucudas.", "author_bot": false, "content": "적절하게 구매하시면 될듯", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:26:16.093000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1401015279424897025", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "924665171010551869", "author_name": "cucudas.", "author_bot": false, "content": "대충 한 달 30일 잡으면 27000구슬", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:34:32.220000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1401015389210542222", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "924665171010551869", "author_name": "cucudas.", "author_bot": false, "content": "현석파편 40 * 120개 + 모방결정체  20 * 30개 * 4주 +에이지스(캐릭,명륜) = 20200구슬", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:34:58.395000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:39:27.295000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1401015594119069736", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "924665171010551869", "author_name": "cucudas.", "author_bot": false, "content": "남는 구슬은 필요한 거 사심 되는데, 초반엔 캐릭 풀 늘려야하니 오리타, 에리카도 사는 걸 추천드리고", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:35:47.249000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1401016025268359348", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "924665171010551869", "author_name": "cucudas.", "author_bot": false, "content": "깃펜도 중요하긴 한데, 사실 깃펜은 그냥 상점에 '다루기내 보급' 효율이 너무 좋아졌어요.", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:37:30.043000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1401016098496839813", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "924665171010551869", "author_name": "cucudas.", "author_bot": false, "content": "기존에는 깃펜도 필수로 샀는데 이젠 잘 안사게 되네요.", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:37:47.502000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1401016952608129085", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "924665171010551869", "author_name": "cucudas.", "author_bot": false, "content": "유우하시 공격 좋아하는데 방어해서 그런가 ㅋㅋ 그런 디테일이 있군요", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:41:11.138000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1401017412798779532", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "924665171010551869", "author_name": "cucudas.", "author_bot": false, "content": "구슬상점에 '재변화'라는 비밀계약도 있을텐데, 얘도 언젠간 필수로 얻을 녀석이에요. 참고해주세요", "timestamp": "2025-08-02T01:43:00.856000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
